This project splits the files into the following directories:

Prompts
for each prompt file:
  - The first line contains the prompt which should be given to the model.
  - The second line contains the preview fully qualified name of a method annotated with both @Composable and @Preview that this prompt refers to.

Screenshots
- Contains screenshots from the preview after applying the user prompt.

Patches
- Contains the source code diff which the model should use when applying the prompt.

Src
- Contains the source code.